tsm2arc reads InfluxDB 1.x TSM and WAL files. The on-disk format decoders are
clean-room implementations in Go based on the publicly documented, stable
InfluxDB 1.x storage format. InfluxDB is a trademark of InfluxData, Inc.;
tsm2arc is not affiliated with or endorsed by InfluxData.

Third-party dependencies are listed in go.mod and their licenses are reproduced
in the generated SBOM attached to each release.
